---
import BaseLayout from "src/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import CTA from "@components/CTA.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Roof Installation"
  description="Expert roof installation services to protect and enhance your home"
>

  <!-- ============================================ -->
  <!--                    LANDING                   -->
  <!-- ============================================ -->

  <section id="int-hero">
    <h1 id="home-h">Roof Installation</h1>
    <picture>
      <source
        media="(max-width: 600px)"
        srcset="/assets/images/landing-cr-new-mobile.jpg"
      />
      <source
        media="(min-width: 601px)"
        srcset="/assets/images/landing-cr-new.jpg"
      />
      <img
        aria-hidden="true"
        decoding="async"
        src="/assets/images/landing-cr-new.jpg"
        alt="drone roof"
        loading="eager"
        width="1440"
        height="455"
      />
    </picture>
  </section>


  <style>
    @media (max-width: 1023px) {
      #int-hero {
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }
    }
  </style>


  <!-- ============================================ -->
<!--             Side By Side Reverse             -->
<!-- ============================================ -->

<section id="sbs-r-870">
    <div class="cs-container">
      <!-- Image Wrapper for Stacking -->
      <div class="cs-images-wrapper">
        <!-- First Image -->
        <picture class="cs-picture">
          <!--Mobile Image-->
          <source media="(max-width: 600px)" srcset="/assets/images/roof-lift-cr.jpg">
          <!--Tablet and above Image-->
          <source media="(min-width: 601px)" srcset="/assets/images/roof-lift-cr.jpg">
          <img
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            src="/assets/images/roof-lift-cr.jpg"
            alt="roof lift"
            width="602"
            height="905"
          >
        </picture>
  
        <!-- Second Image -->
        <picture class="cs-picture">
          <!--Mobile Image-->
          <source media="(max-width: 600px)" srcset="/assets/images/roof-install-1.jpg">
          <!--Tablet and above Image-->
          <source media="(min-width: 601px)" srcset="/assets/images/roof-install-1.jpg">
          <img
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            src="/assets/images/roof-install-1.jpg"
            alt="roof installation"
            width="630"
            height="903"
          >
        </picture>
  
         <!-- Second Image -->
         <picture class="cs-picture">
          <!--Mobile Image-->
          <source media="(max-width: 600px)" srcset="/assets/images/hammer-cr.jpg">
          <!--Tablet and above Image-->
          <source media="(min-width: 601px)" srcset="/assets/images/hammer-cr.jpg">
          <img
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            src="/assets/images/hammer-cr.jpg"
            alt="hammering"
            width="630"
            height="775"
          >
        </picture>
      </div>
  
  <!-- Content Section -->
<div class="cs-content">
  <span class="cs-topper">Featured Service</span>
  <h2 class="cs-title">Roof Installation</h2>
  <p class="cs-text">
    Keep your home both secure and attractive with professional roof installation solutions. Whether constructing a new residence, replacing an aging rooftop, or refreshing your property, our proficient crew provides top-grade results. Emphasizing resilience and visual charm, we present roofing systems customized to meet the distinct demands of your property and surroundings.
  </p>

  <h3>Why Choose Our Roof Installation Services?</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Seasoned and Qualified Roofers:</strong> Our crew is made up of accredited and well-trained roofing specialists who take pride in delivering first-rate installation work. We tackle each undertaking with accuracy, guaranteeing your roof is placed with exceptional attention to detail and skill.</li>
    <li><strong>Top-Grade Components:</strong> We rely solely on premium materials to ensure the durability and efficiency of your roofing system. From long-lasting asphalt shingles to sustainable metal coverings, we provide a range of options to match your preferences and finances, all while boosting your home’s visual allure.</li>
    <li><strong>All-Encompassing Setup Procedures:</strong> Our approach is meticulous and open, spanning initial consultations and accurate roof sizing through to the last assessment. We devote the necessary attention to every aspect, ensuring a seamless, worry-free process on your end.</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Our Roof Installation Services</h3>
  <h4>New Roof Installations</h4>
  <p class="cs-text">
    For fresh building endeavors, our roofing installation offerings lay a robust groundwork to shield your residence. We provide:
    <ul>
      <li>Specialized guidance in selecting the ideal roof system for your dwelling.</li>
      <li>Precise dimensions and comprehensive roof schematics to guarantee a flawless result.</li>
      <li>Swift setup utilizing top-notch materials engineered to endure severe environmental factors.</li>
    </ul>
  </p>

  <h4>Roof Replacement Services</h4>
  <p class="cs-text">
    Is your aging roof displaying deterioration? Our replacement solution revitalizes your home with a new top layer that appears outstanding and functions even more effectively. Key features include:
    <ul>
      <li>In-depth evaluations to ascertain if a full replacement is warranted.</li>
      <li>Careful removal of the existing structure and responsible material disposal.</li>
      <li>Fitting a new roof that aligns with your personal requirements and style inclinations.</li>
    </ul>
  </p>

  <h4>Roof Installation for Various Roof Types</h4>
  <p class="cs-text">
    We provide dedicated installation services for an array of roof styles, such as:
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Sloped Roofs:</strong> A classic option ensuring superb water runoff and enduring appeal.</li>
      <li><strong>Level Roofs:</strong> Suited for contemporary residences, delivering a streamlined appearance and low-maintenance surface.</li>
      <li><strong>Peaked and Hipped Roofs:</strong> Combining practicality and aesthetics with improved structural steadiness.</li>
    </ul>
  </p>

  <h4>Emergency Roof Installation Services</h4>
  <p class="cs-text">
    In urgent circumstances, our emergency installation services secure your home swiftly against environmental threats. Be it storm aftermath, unforeseen incidents, or sudden deterioration, we respond promptly to fit a new roof and avert additional complications.
  </p>

  <h4>Roof Installation Process</h4>
  <p class="cs-text">
    Our installation method is crafted for speed and reassurance:
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Consultation & Strategy:</strong> We start by assessing your requirements, providing expert recommendations on materials and designs. Additionally, we deliver a precise quote and schedule for the project.</li>
      <li><strong>Area Prep & Clearance:</strong> In cases of replacement, our team securely strips the old layers and readies your house for the new roof. We prioritize safeguarding your property and maintaining cleanliness during the entire endeavor.</li>
      <li><strong>Roof Assembly:</strong> Our seasoned crew will promptly put in the new structure, attending closely to each element. Whether your choice is timeless shingles or sustainable metal panels, we guarantee a precise and smooth setup.</li>
      <li><strong>Final Review & Tidying:</strong> After completion, we run a meticulous inspection to confirm adherence to standards and your satisfaction. Our team tidies up fully, restoring your property’s original neat condition.</li>
    </ul>
  </p>

  <p class="cs-text">
    We provide adaptable appointment options, including weekend availability, to accommodate your lifestyle. Furthermore, we present financing plans for budget-friendly and hassle-free installations. You can trust us to supply premier roofing at fair rates, safeguarding your property without straining your finances.
  </p>

  <p class="cs-text">
    Take the first step now by arranging your no-cost consultation, and let us assist in achieving the perfect roof for you. Whether constructing anew or enhancing an old design, we bring the skill and excellence needed to fulfill your vision.
  </p>
  <a href="/services/roof-repairs" class="cs-button-solid">Roof Repairs</a>
</div>
</div>
</section>

  
  
  <style>
    /*-- -------------------------- -->
  <---    Side By Side Reverse    -->
  <--- -------------------------- -*/
  
  /*-- -------------------------- -->
  <---    Side By Side Reverse    -->
  <--- -------------------------- -*/
  
  /* Mobile - 360px */
  @media only screen and (min-width: 0rem) {
      #sbs-r-870 {
          padding: var(--sectionPadding);
      }
      #sbs-r-870 .cs-container {
          width: 100%;
          max-width: 34.375rem; /* 550px */
          margin: auto;
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: center;
          gap: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 4rem);
      }
      
      #sbs-r-870 .cs-picture {
    width: 100%; /* Full width of the parent container */
    max-width: 39.375rem; /* Maximum width (e.g., 630px) */
    height: 39.375rem; /* Set height equal to the width to create a square */
    box-shadow: 0px 2.8px 42px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16);
    border-radius: 5%; /* Fully rounded corners, turning it into a circle */
    overflow: hidden;
    align-self: flex-start; /* Ensure the image stays at the top */
    margin-bottom:7rem; /* Add spacing below the image */
}


      #sbs-r-870 .cs-picture img {
          width: 100%;
          height: 100%;
          object-fit: cover;
      }
      #sbs-r-870 .cs-content {
          text-align: left;
          max-width: 33.875rem; /* 542px */
          box-sizing: border-box;
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: flex-start;
          gap: 1.5rem; /* Add spacing between elements */
          padding: 1.5rem; /* Add padding inside the content area */
      }
      #sbs-r-870 .cs-content h3 {
          font-size: 1.5rem;
          font-weight: bold;
          margin-bottom: 1rem; /* Space below headings */
      }
      #sbs-r-870 .cs-content h4 {
          font-size: 1.25rem;
          font-weight: bold;
          margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      }
      #sbs-r-870 .cs-content p {
          line-height: 1.8; /* Improve readability */
          margin-bottom: 1rem; /* Space between paragraphs */
      }
      #sbs-r-870 .cs-content ul {
          list-style-type: disc; /* Add bullet points */
          padding-left: 1.5rem; /* Indent list items */
          margin-bottom: 1.5rem; /* Space below the list */
      }
      #sbs-r-870 .cs-content ul li {
          margin-bottom: 0.75rem; /* Space between list items */
      }
      #sbs-r-870 .cs-button-solid {
          font-size: 1rem;
          line-height: clamp(2.875rem, 5.5vw, 3.5rem);
          text-decoration: none;
          font-weight: 700;
          text-align: center;
          margin-top: 2rem; /* Add spacing above the button */
          color: #fff;
          min-width: 9.375rem;
          padding: 0 1.5rem;
          background-color: var(--primary);
          border-radius: 0.25rem;
          display: inline-block;
          position: relative;
          z-index: 1;
          box-sizing: border-box;
      }
      #sbs-r-870 .cs-button-solid:before {
          content: "";
          position: absolute;
          height: 100%;
          width: 0%;
          background: #000;
          opacity: 1;
          top: 0;
          left: 0;
          z-index: -1;
          border-radius: 0.25rem;
          transition: width 0.3s;
      }
      #sbs-r-870 .cs-button-solid:hover:before {
          width: 100%;
      }
  }
  
  /* Desktop - 1024px */
  @media only screen and (min-width: 64rem) {
      #sbs-r-870 {
          padding: var(--sectionPadding);
      }
  
      #sbs-r-870 .cs-container {
          flex-direction: row; /* Preserve side-by-side layout for content */
          max-width: 80rem; /* 1280px */
          justify-content: space-between;
          align-items: flex-start; /* Align everything to the top */
      }
  
      #sbs-r-870 .cs-images-wrapper {
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: column; /* Stack images vertically */
          width: 47%; /* Ensure images wrapper occupies the same space as before */
          gap: 5.6rem; /* Maintain spacing between stacked images */
          align-self: flex-start; /* Ensure the images wrapper starts at the top */
      }
  
      #sbs-r-870 .cs-content {
          width: 53%; /* Retain content width */
          padding: 0;
          order: 1; /* Move content to the right */
      }
  
      #sbs-r-870 .cs-picture {
          width: 100%; /* Ensure images fill the wrapper */
          height: auto; /* Maintain aspect ratio */
      }
  
      #sbs-r-870 .cs-picture img {
          display: block; /* Prevent inline spacing issues */
          width: 100%; /* Ensure image takes full width of its container */
          height: auto; /* Maintain natural aspect ratio */
          object-fit: cover; /* Ensure content fits within the container */
      }
  }
  
  
  
  </style>

  <CTA />
</BaseLayout>

